---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---
<MainLayout title="Verkada Workplace | Blue Cap IT — Gold Partner" description="Blue Cap IT deploys Verkada Workplace solutions — visitor management, mailroom tracking, badge printing, and guest pre-registration. Official Verkada Gold Partner. Call (410) 858-4031.">
  <div class="inner-hero">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="crumbs"><a href="index.html">Home</a> <span>/</span> <a href="verkada.html">Verkada Solutions</a> <span>/</span> Workplace</div>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:3rem;align-items:center;">
        <div>
          <div class="section-label">Verkada Solution</div>
          <h1>Verkada <span class="grad">Workplace</span></h1>
          <p class="section-sub">A complete visitor management and workplace platform — digital check-in, mailroom tracking, badge printing, and seamless access control integration, all managed through Verkada Command.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:2rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
            <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost btn-sm"><Icon name="lucide:phone" /> (410) 858-4031</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <img src="/workplace-hero.png" alt="Verkada Workplace visitor management" style="width:100%;border-radius:1rem;" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div style="text-align:center;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto 4rem;">
        <div class="section-label">Why Verkada Workplace</div>
        <h2>Smarter Visitor &amp; Workplace<br/><span class="grad">Management</span></h2>
        <p class="section-sub" style="text-align:center;margin:0.8rem auto 0;">Verkada Workplace replaces paper sign-in sheets and disconnected tools with a single cloud-managed platform for visitors, deliveries, and employee credentials.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-list">
        <div class="feature-row">
          <div class="feature-visual"><div class="feature-visual-bg"></div><img src="/verkada/workplace/guest-checkin.jpg" alt="Verkada Workplace guest check-in mockup" style="max-width:380px;width:100%;border-radius:8px;filter:drop-shadow(0 16px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.2));" /></div>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h3>Digital Visitor Check-In</h3>
            <p>Replace clipboards with a professional iPad kiosk experience. Visitors check in digitally, sign NDAs, print badges, and automatically notify their host — all in under a minute.</p>
            <ul class="feature-bullets">
              <li>iPad-based kiosk for lobby check-in</li>
              <li>Custom NDA and legal document signing</li>
              <li>Automatic badge printing on arrival</li>
              <li>Instant host notifications via email, SMS, or Slack</li>
              <li>Branded check-in experience with your company logo</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-row rev">
          <div class="feature-visual"><div class="feature-visual-bg"></div><img src="/verkada/workplace/mailroom.jpg" alt="Verkada Workplace mailroom management on laptop and mobile" style="max-width:380px;width:100%;border-radius:8px;filter:drop-shadow(0 16px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.2));" /></div>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h3>Mailroom &amp; Package Management</h3>
            <p>Scan, log, and track every package that enters your building. Recipients are automatically notified, and you have a complete chain-of-custody record for every delivery.</p>
            <ul class="feature-bullets">
              <li>Barcode scanning for instant package logging</li>
              <li>Automatic recipient notification</li>
              <li>Full delivery chain-of-custody tracking</li>
              <li>Pickup confirmation and audit trail</li>
              <li>Reduce lost and misdelivered packages</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-row">
          <div class="feature-visual"><div class="feature-visual-bg"></div><img src="/verkada/workplace/dl-scan.jpg" alt="Verkada Workplace driver's license scanning for guest registration" style="max-width:380px;width:100%;border-radius:8px;filter:drop-shadow(0 16px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.2));" /></div>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h3>Guest Pre-Registration &amp; QR Code Access</h3>
            <p>Employees can pre-register guests ahead of time. Visitors receive a QR code via email that lets them check in instantly on arrival — no waiting in line.</p>
            <ul class="feature-bullets">
              <li>Pre-register visitors from desktop or mobile</li>
              <li>Guests receive QR code before arrival</li>
              <li>Scan-to-check-in for a frictionless experience</li>
              <li>Pre-approved visitors skip the full registration flow</li>
              <li>Calendar integration for scheduled meetings</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-row rev">
          <div class="feature-visual"><div class="feature-visual-bg"></div><img src="/verkada/workplace/background-check.png" alt="Verkada Workplace background check screen" style="max-width:380px;width:100%;border-radius:8px;filter:drop-shadow(0 16px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.2));" /></div>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h3>Background Checks &amp; Access Control Integration</h3>
            <p>Screen visitors against watchlists and run background checks before granting access. Verkada Workplace integrates directly with Verkada access control for seamless door unlock upon check-in.</p>
            <ul class="feature-bullets">
              <li>Background check integration for visitor screening</li>
              <li>Watchlist alerts for flagged individuals</li>
              <li>Automatic temporary access credentials on check-in</li>
              <li>Access revoked automatically on checkout</li>
              <li>All managed through Verkada Command</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="specs-section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">Workplace Features</div>
      <h2>Verkada Workplace <span class="grad">Capabilities</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Everything you need to manage visitors, deliveries, and employee credentials in one platform.</p>
      <div class="products-grid">
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><img src="/verkada/workplace/guest-iphone.jpg" alt="Visitor check-in on iPhone" style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:8px;object-fit:cover;" /></div>
          <h3>Visitor Management</h3>
          <p>Digital check-in kiosk with NDA signing, host notifications, and a complete visitor log — replacing paper sign-in sheets with a professional, secure experience.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><img src="/verkada/workplace/reception-ui.png" alt="Mailroom reception UI" style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:8px;object-fit:cover;" /></div>
          <h3>Mailroom Management</h3>
          <p>Scan and track every package from arrival to pickup. Recipients are notified automatically, and every handoff is logged for accountability.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><img src="/verkada/workplace/guest-printer.png" alt="Guest badge printer" style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:8px;object-fit:cover;" /></div>
          <h3>Badge Printing</h3>
          <p>Print visitor and employee badges on demand. Badges include photo, name, host, and expiration — making it easy to identify who belongs in your building.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><img src="/verkada/workplace/guest-checkin.jpg" alt="Guest check-in" style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:8px;object-fit:cover;" /></div>
          <h3>Guest Pre-Registration</h3>
          <p>Employees pre-register visitors ahead of time. Guests receive a QR code for instant check-in on arrival — no lines, no delays.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><img src="/verkada/workplace/background-check.png" alt="Background check" style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:8px;object-fit:cover;" /></div>
          <h3>Background Checks</h3>
          <p>Screen visitors against watchlists and run background checks before granting building access. Stay compliant and keep your people safe.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:door-open" /></div>
          <h3>Access Integration</h3>
          <p>Verkada Workplace connects directly to Verkada access control. Visitors receive temporary credentials at check-in that are automatically revoked at checkout.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="cta-band">
    <div class="section-label">Upgrade Your Front Desk</div>
    <h2>Modern Visitor Management by<br/><span class="grad">Blue Cap IT</span></h2>
    <p>We deploy and configure Verkada Workplace for your building — from kiosk setup to access control integration. Contact us for a free quote.</p>
    <div class="btn-group">
      <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
      <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost"><Icon name="lucide:phone" /> (410) 858-4031</a>
      <a href="mailto:info@bluecapit.com" class="btn-ghost"><Icon name="lucide:mail" /> info@bluecapit.com</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
